high_descs: Turn right and move to the counter near the teapot.
Pick up the sharp knife that is near the egg.
Turn right and move to the counter where the bread is.
Use the knife to slice the bread.
Turn left and move to the microwave.
Place the knife into the microwave.
Turn right, move to the counter where the bread is.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn left and move to the microwave.
Place the bread slice into the microwave, cook the bread slice, remove the bread slice.
Turn right, move to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the bread slice on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of bread into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the end of the island.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn to the right and begin to walk toward the dishwasher.
Walk closer to the dishwasher.
Turn to the left and walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the knife on the plate
Close the microwave, turn right, and walk toward the sink.
Pick up a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place bread on plate in the microwave, warm the bread, and then remove the bread from the microwave.
Turn to the right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the bread slice inside.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm slice of bread into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Go to the table by the window.
Pick up the chef's knife on the table.
Go to the dishwasher.
Slice the bread with the knife.
Move to the microwave.
Put the chef's knife in the microwave.
Move back to the counter over the dishwasher.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Move back to the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave.
Go to the fridge.
Put the warm bread into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm piece of bread in the refrigerator.
